Class AlchemyVision

java.lang.Object

public class AlchemyVision
extends AlchemyService

The Alchemy Vision service uses deep learning innovations to understand a picture’s content and context. It sees complex visual scenes in their entirety —without needing any textual clues— leveraging a holistic approach to understanding the multiple objects and surroundings.

public ImageFaces recognizeFaces(Map<String,Object> params)
Recognize faces from an image or url. For each face detected returns:
  • bounding box
  • gender
  • approximate age
  • name (if celebrity is detected)
